{{italic title}} '''''Atmosphere''''' is the biannual [[inflight magazine]] of [[Air Transat]], one of the [[airlines]] operating in [[Canada]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Air Transat In-Flight Magazine Atmosphere|url=http://www.duanestorey.com/journal/air-transat-in-flight-magazine/|work=The Duane Storey|accessdate=6 September 2016|date=10 January 2008}}</ref>
==History and profile== ''Atmosphere'' was founded in 2006 and the first issue was published in March 2006.<ref name="airt">{{cite news|title=Something new in the sky: Atmosphere magazine launched on Air Transat|url=http://news-releases.transat.com/2006-03-01-Air-Transat-Something-new-in-the-sky-Atmosphere-magazine-launched-on-Air-Transat|accessdate=6 September 2016|work=Air Transat|date=1 March 2006|location=Montreal}}</ref> The magazine is published in English and in French.<ref name="airt"/> The publisher is Business Class Media.<ref name="airt"/> Formerly, it was published on a quarterly basis, but now it is published biannually.<ref>{{cite news|title=New edition of Atmosphere magazine now on board Air Transat flights|url=http://news-releases.transat.com/New-edition-of-Atmosphere-magazine-now-on-board-Air-Transat-flights|accessdate=6 September 2016|work=Air Transat|date=2 June 2016}}</ref>
